e<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Donald<br>Trump (R)\n! Oprah<br>Winfrey (D)\n! Other\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.scribd.com/document/368950464/POLL-TRUMP-VS-OPRAH Dixie Strategies]\n| Jan 9\u201310, 2018\n| 785\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.5%\n| {{party shading/Republican}}| '''48%'''\n| 24%\n| 15%\n| 13%\n|}\n\n;with Donald Trump and generic Democrat\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Donald<br>Trump (R)\n! Generic<br>Democrat\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.lcv.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/FL-LCV-Memo-June-19.pdf Public Policy Polling (D)]{{efn|Poll sponsored by the [[League of Conservation Voters]]|name=\"LCV\"}}\n| Jun 14\u201316, 2019\n| 679\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.8%\n| 44%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}| '''51%'''\n| 6%\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.politico.com/f/?id=00000168-7cef-de11-af7d-feff7b080001 Mason-Dixon]\n| Jan 14\u201317, 2019\n| 625\n| \u00b1&nbsp;4.0%\n| 45%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}| '''46%'''\n| 9%\n|}\n\n;with Mike Pence and Joe Biden\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|name=key}}\n! Margin<br>{{nowrap|of error}}\n! Mike<br>Pence (R)\n! Joe<br>Biden (D)\n! Other\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.unf.edu/publicrelations/media_relations/press/2019/New_UNF_Poll_Reveals_Florida_Torn_Over_Trump_Impeachment_Inquiry.aspx University of North Florida]\n| Oct 14-20, 2019\n| 643 (RV)\n| \u00b1&nbsp;3.8%\n|39%\n|{{party shading/Democratic}}|'''49%'''\n|8%{{efn|Wouldn't vote with 8%}}\n|5%\n|}\n\n;with Mike Pence and Elizabeth Warren\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valig